-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Gridx - Incubation for the next generation of Grid
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author: Xiao Wen Zhu(Oliver), Pei Wang(Nate), Masato Noguchi, Wei Huang(Evan), Qiang Wang(Elvis)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description:

	Gridx is an incubation project as a basis for the next generation of Dojo Grid.
	The key idea is to set up a highly extensible core and a rich set of modules to be loaded on demand.
	Appropriate modules can be picked up to consist different Grid instances(e.g MiniGrid/MobileGrid, AdvancedGrid etc),
	and this makes it possible to meet a wide range of requirements.

	Please try the demo and see how Gridx is running more faster and flexible!
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

	Dojo Core
	Dijit
	Dojox (mobile)
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions

	Simply run the included demo.html
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
